Source.Contents:
/#
 The code specification of whether a trade is settling using standard settlement instructions as well as whether it is a candidate for settlement netting.
 #/
enum FpML5.confirmation.StandardSettlementStyleEnum {
    # This trade will settle using standard pre-determined funds settlement instructions.
    Standard 
    # This trade is a candidate for settlement netting.
    Net 
    # This trade will settle using standard pre-determined funds settlement instructions and is a candidate for settlement netting.
    StandardAndNet 

}

Standard.Doc: This trade will settle using standard pre-determined funds settlement instructions.
Standard.Name: Standard

Net.Doc: This trade is a candidate for settlement netting.
Net.Name: Net

StandardAndNet.Doc: This trade will settle using standard pre-determined funds settlement instructions and is a candidate for settlement netting.
StandardAndNet.Name: StandardAndNet
